MONGODB EXTENDED SHELL ANALYTICS TOOLS AND FUNCTIONS

* uses `~/.mongorc.js` to preload the libraries
* use `mongo --norc` to skip loading `~/.mongorc.js`

Usage
  1 /path/to/this/gem/bin/mongolita-install
  2 ./mongo

